{"text": "First of all, I hate most of FPS, and I also hate most of games with zombies on it, nevertheless this game is in overall, something really fun, you just don't go smashing and blasting random stuff like in other games (doesn't mean you can't do that here too though), but you have to cooperate with the other survivors to be able to get through, survivors can be either players or bots, but if you don't like working with others, well, there are other game modes including one in which you have to go on your own. This game provides some challenge, and also different kinds of zombies to fight against, from smokers who will pull you to tanks that will smash you if you're not careful. Another point to notice is the workshop, full of nice mods/skins to improve/change your game experience.", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198113516735", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1414411200.0}
