{"text": "Kingdom Rush ist ein wirklich empfehlenswertes Tower Defense Game. Man spielt ausschlieÃŸ solo gegen die KI. Es gibt einen Kampagnen-, Heroic- und Ironmodus auf jeder Map. Das Spiel hat alles, was ein TD-Klassiker braucht. Manchmal wÃ¤re es nicht schlecht wenn sich die Spielgeschwindigkeit erhÃ¶hen lieÃŸe, da die Gegner teils ziemlich langsam sind. Kleiner Tip: Wenn man alle Achievements sammeln mÃ¶chte, muss man die Level auf Schwierigkeit Normal spielen.", "appid": "246420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198031186123", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518264000.0}
{"text": "Ok so I have spent a fair deal of time playing this game. As for the state of the game at the time of this review (7/19/20) Its pretty... ok... I guess. This game has taken a series of twists and turns for me, some of these have had better outcomes than others. So a bit of backstory on my history of this game. The very first time I played this game was in the spring of 2016, near the release of the legend Diana. however initially I wasn't too fond of this game, so I didn't really play it therefore it sat in my library to collect dust, similarly to some of my other games that I haven't touched. eventually during the summer of 2018 I decided to revist the game after all this time and boy am i glad I did, I was hooked on this game, I simply couldn't put it down. I was having a tremendous amount of fun playing this game. After a while I decided to try my luck at ranked. initially I was pretty bad at it getting stuck around Silver 3/4. but nevertheless I kept trying and with time and practice I started to get a bit better. I still remember the moment that I hit gold rank for the first time. It was the best feeling, something that I had been working toward had finally been achieved. This game makes you work for things that you want but when you finally achieve those things this game gives you that \"sense of accomplishment\" that most other games have an abscence of. throughout my time in ranked my main goal has been to reach platinum and i've come so close getting all the way to Gold 5 but I've never been able to persevere through that final stretch. I would reccomend this game to new players... in a heartbeat. but this game does a really proficient job at roping you in, so be warned you will play this game until you are sick of it.", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198061892266", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595160000.0}
