{"text": "About the game itself Pros - One of the best story telling game I've ever play - Pretty good graphic - Beautiful musics Note : You may need some tissues while you're playing this game Cons - Not much things to do ( Move to where the game tell you to go there, some easy puzzles ) - Reading the converstion the whole game ( Pass this game if you don't like reading ) - Short story ( You can finish it within 2-4 hrs depending on your reading skill xD ) 10/10 For me, since I don't mind reading, I love the musics ( it force me to buy the soundtracks after I've finish the game )  My personal opinions / experiences - Got this game for half a year and never try it, until one of my friend told me that I must try it. Not sure where I got this game, but it was a part of MOST bundle games in my library, which mean I got this game in real cheap price, but it was an only bundle games I've ever play and feel like \" Can't believe a bundle game was so good, it's almost made me cry ~\". It's just more awesome than bundle games. . . - I'm not usually write a reviews for games, This was my second reviews of all. but I just can't stop thinking why don't just put reviews on this games it tooo awesome ~ - As I meantions above, If you willing to get the game, believe me, just get it with the soundtracks, because you're going to get it after you've finish it anyway.", "appid": "206440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198107117107", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435060800.0}
