{"text": "Fallout New Vegas is one of my most favorite games ever.  It's just as amazing as Fallout 3, but the game is a bit on the lighter side astmosphere wise. Instead of taking place on the east coast like Fallout 3, This takes place on the west coast and gives the game that more cowboy southern feel to it. I also find the story to be a tad more enjoyable just because it's so different and refreshing from Fallout 3. I'm normally not a fan of shooter games, but Fallout is amazing! I suggest you give this game a try, I'm sure it will be one of your favorites in no time!", "appid": "22380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035697954", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "57", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1392292800.0}
