{"text": "I have mixed feelings about this game.because at times its fun and at times it can be boring. This game has a singleplayer which is done in a rush and its just there for pople who wants to know the story. So in short the singleplayer is nothing special. Then you have the multiplayer, which is fun, you can play with 8 players on 6 diffrent maps (the maps looks the same only the structures are in diffrent locations) and many diffrent difficulty modes. There are 15 waves and each wave has diffrent enemy types which spawn  at 5 diffrent locations on the map. So if you dont stick to your group you can get overrun by the mobs of creatures. So when you play all the maps and done most of the modes then it can get boring. There are poeple who love it but for some people it has not enough content to keep them intrested. The game is hard at times but nothing unbeatable whit a good team. PROS Creates tense moments. Nice skills and classes to choose from. Relies on teamwork (which is nice) CONS Can get boring at times. Needs more diffent content I really dont know if i liked this game or disliked it, its just a mixed feeling that i have of this game. 6.5/10", "appid": "265590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198020930198", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1436788800.0}
