{"text": "Colorful game and with a sense of humour, however without a player base. You can still encounter some vets between 8PM and 1AM CST.  I managed to play several PvP games, such as Deathmatch and Team Deathmatch but couldn't get to Capture the Flag, since no one was available for that game mode. Furthermore, you can't change your region, at least for now. It's a simple game made for fun, so don't expect a Call of Duty for 10 bucks.  According to some topics posted on the game's discussion board, devs are expecting to get a player base after the audience will get bored of PUBG or Fortnite. Anyway, won't rate this one negative, since devs are actually listening and trying to make things better, plus I really enjoyed running around in my banana orc costume.", "appid": "622170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044606882", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517745600.0}
