{"text": "I wanted this game before, then I forgot about it and finally my friend told me it's free, so I'm really happy I have it. This is some survival style game, where you can play with your friends, random players or alone and survive zombie hordes, build barricades, buy new weapons and wait for sale (only people who played it will understand). Game is as easy as it looks, but the more nights pass, the  harder it is to survive, and finally zombies will be too overpowered to kill them. Also you can play Endless mode, where you need to survive as long as you can without buying anything, upgrading skills or building. If you don't like just shooting zombies - go play another game mode called deathmatch, where you can kill real players and protect yourself from zombies at the same time, It's really fun to do it. Game looks fine, didn't found any bugs yet, never lags. You can also buy game called ,,Yet Another Zombie Defense HD \" for better graphics, but I'm okay with my current settings, maybe I'll get it in future. Game is tottaly recommended for playing with friends few times a day, I'm still not bored to play it. RECCOMENDED", "appid": "270550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198216675732", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1526212800.0}
{"text": "So far I have been looking into this gaem, it would seem quite good. Only minor issue is the lack of players, meaning getting into a match can take a tad before it happens. But that being said, each ship is acquired through either playing the game or paying to get the ship.  (Now bear in mind I have only recently started playing so I do not know if there's real Pay-To-Win features, but so far none spotted!) Therefore, I do recommend the game.  - Good Gameplay - Good Graphics - Good FPS  - Great fun when played with friends - Cordination and coperation is essential to win.  I'll see in due time if I require to update my review or not. This is all for now!", "appid": "310380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198031966660", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1472385600.0}
