ith it Bugs: =>Respawn timer disapearing when you are checking the scoreboard, or changing class =>Music sometimes disapearing when you go back to the menu after finishing a battle  And finally but not last : Please bring the terminators and it varient to the game, doesn't mater if some of you thinks the design suck ass from what i heard, as long as it isnt locked behind expensive pay-wall,is balanced, we will be happy to see them While i frequently play the game and SOMETIMES enjoying it, i cannot recommend in it current state.", "appid": "375230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198195976589", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1570968000.0}
