{"text": "Ironically it was the \"Out of the Blue\" patch that was the final nail in the coffin for this game for me.  Removing classes?  Completely disrupting the balance of the game?  What were they thinking?  If I had my wish some other developer should purchase the rights to the Tribes franchise and start off by bringing this game back as it was before the OotB patch.  At the very least they should allow for unofficial dedicated servers to do the same.  It's pretty telling that they even asked Steam to de-list the game which is them essentially trying to sweep it under the rug and forget about it.  The Tribes franchise deserves far more respect that Hi-Rez gave it and they are not worthy of holding the franchise rights.  I'll never touch another game of theirs until they rectify this situation.", "appid": "17080", "steamid": "profiles/76561197967682771", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "15", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594382400.0}
