{"text": "OK! I think now I played enough to write a fair review of this game. this is the second time that I'm writing a review for this game and last time it I did recommend this game but now let's take  look at this game again. * Toxic community: The community of this game is honestly the most TOXIC and ANNOYING one I ever experienced in my life but this is not a positive or a negative thing (so if you like to be toxic, this game is for you and if you don't like to be toxic or get bullied so it's not your type of game) * Characters: there are 20 killers and 22 survivors, you may like some of them or hate them, it depends on the players. * It's the most balance and most populated game of it's style with a lot of interesting events going on every now and then * a lot of licensed DLCs that make the game interesting  * a lot of perks that make different gameplays every match * Matchmaking: not gonna lie the matchmaking was bad sometimes before the new update but now after the new update, it's trash (imagine that you just bought the game and after 2 game you have to play against the players that played this game more than 1k hours and are in the top ranks, or you are pro and have to play against or with low rank players that don't even know the basics of the game) * Bugs and glitches: man this game is full of bugs and every patch fix updates fix 1 bug and add like 3 other bugs to the game (they just recently launched the 4th anniversary event and even the event items were buggy and glitchy and almost everything in game wasn't working correctly! after 4 years experience) * Annoying errors: this game filled by errors. connection error even if there is nothing wrong with your connection, matchmaking error, host connection error, rank update error, there is even an error that they don't even know what is it and they call it unknown error :D (recently there was sync error 111 in the game that they fixed it and after that you get sync error 112 :| ) * Bad servers * Bad hit boxes So as a gamer I do recommend this game, give it a try but as a player of this game I really don't  . all the new updates are bad and annoying. for the new players when they see a new chapter it's like wow a new killer but for us it's like S*** new bugs. But as i said sadly you won't find any other game based on this style and find it more balanced than this. P.R: 5/10 Kill Claudette !!!!", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198366848246", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0}
